55 received at least 45 days before the November 3, 2026 state election, not later than Saturday,
56 September 19, 2026.
57 SECTION 9. Notwithstanding any general or special law to the contrary, the state
58 secretary may add or change any dates relating to the nominations made at the September 1,
59 2026 state primary that the state secretary considers necessary for the orderly administration of
